  description="Regulatory disclosures and compliance information for Heidi Blondin Financial. Mutual funds offered through Investia Financial Services Inc."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-16">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Website Compliance</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose-hbf">

        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Investia-mandated website compliance disclaimer -->
        <!-- This content must be populated with the verbatim Investia-approved compliance text -->
        <!-- Any changes require Investia compliance pre-approval before launch -->

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 p-5 mb-8">
          <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-1">Content placeholder — Investia compliance required</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-amber-700">The Investia-mandated website compliance disclaimer text must be inserted here verbatim. This content is compliance-mandated and must be preserved exactly as approved by Investia. Please obtain the current approved disclaimer text from Investia and replace this placeholder before site launch.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Website Compliance Disclosures</h2>

        <p><em>[Insert verbatim Investia-approved website compliance disclaimer here. The current live text covers: mutual funds, segregated funds, GICs, life/health insurance, "not personalized advice" language, and "Canadian residents only" language. Obtain the approved text from the Investia compliance contact before launch.]</em></p>

        <h3>Mutual Funds</h3>
        <p>Mutual funds are offered through Investia Financial Services Inc., a member of the Canadian Investor Protection Fund (CIPF) and regulated by the Canadian Investment Regulatory Organization (CIRO).</p>

        <h3>Insurance Products</h3>
        <p>Life insurance, accident and sickness insurance, and other insurance products are offered through Heidi Blondin Financial / Qualified Financial Services.</p>

        <h3>General Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>The information on this website is for general information purposes only and does not constitute personalized financial, investment, tax, or legal advice. Please consult with a qualified financial advisor before making any financial decisions. This website is intended for residents of Canada only.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
